({:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 1}, :title "The Western Sands", :description "The western edge of the desert stretches out before you, a vast sea of shimmering golden sand dunes. The sky is a deep azure, contrasting the arid, untouched sands below. An unbroken horizon lies all around, silent and eerily beautiful.", :exits-description "To the east, the sandy expanse continues, undulating waves of gold disappearing into the heat haze.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The sun beats down, casting long shadows between the dunes.", :night "Under the starlit sky, the desert's tranquillity is amplified.", :dawn "The first light of day paints the sands with a blush of pink and orange.", :dusk "As the sun dips, the sands take on a glow of deep red, like smoldering embers."}, :season {:summer "Heat haze shimmers in the air, adding a mystical quality to the desert.", :winter "Despite the chill, the desert remains unyielding, its sands cold underfoot.", :fall "Winds scatter sand, causing miniature sandstorms between the dunes.", :spring "Tiny sprouts of resilient desert flora peek out from the sand, a rare splash of green in the monotonous gold."}, :weather {:rain "The rare drops of rain create a peculiar yet pleasant petrichor rising from the warm sand.", :snow "The sight of snow on sand is strange, a white veil on the gold.", :fog "Fog here seems impossible yet here it is, shrouding the dunes in mystery.", :sunny "The sun's relentless rays make the sands glitter like a sea of diamonds.", :cloudy "The desert seems quieter under a blanket of clouds.", :partly-cloudy "Partial shade brings a mild respite from the harsh desert sun."}}, :exits {:east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 2}, :flags #{}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 2}, :title "Serpent Dunes", :description "Here, the sand dunes wind like a massive serpentine creature, curving and slithering into the horizon. Their slopes are steep, the sand fine and quick to slip underfoot. Wind-sculpted ridges on the dunes create complex patterns, a testament to the desert's artistic side.", :exits-description "Westward lies the Western Sands, while the dunes continue east into the desert's heart. A hidden passageway to the north opens to an underground cavern.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "Under the bright sun, the dunes appear more like a golden dragon's scales.", :night "The moonlight transforms the dunes into shimmering silver curves.", :dawn "A gentle warmth starts to seep into the cool morning sands.", :dusk "Shadows deepen between the dunes, lending them a solemn beauty."}, :season {:summer "Heat waves distort the horizon, creating mirages of desert oases.", :winter "The cold wind cuts sharply across the dunes, carrying with it grains of chilled sand.", :fall "Occasionally, a lone tumbleweed scuttles past, the desert's only traveler.", :spring "The stillness is periodically broken by the rustle of sand-skippers, the desert's rare insects."}, :weather {:rain "The rain forms transient streams, carving new patterns into the dunes.", :snow "Snowflakes sparkle as they fall onto the sands, a short-lived beauty.", :fog "The fog softens the desert's harsh lines, shrouding the dunes in ethereal beauty.", :sunny "Sunlight catches in the sand, turning the dunes into a blinding sea of light.", :cloudy "The overcast sky lends an unusual gloom to the desert.", :partly-cloudy "Patches of sunlight play a mesmerizing game of hide and seek on the dunes."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 1}, :flags #{}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 3}, :flags #{}}, :north {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 20}, :flags #{:hidden}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 3}, :title "The Silent Plateau", :description "A vast flat expanse of sandstone lies here, unyielding to the desert winds. Tiny grains of sand skitter across the plateau, creating faint, whispering sounds. The emptiness is punctuated by a single, ancient acacia tree standing defiantly in the vastness.", :exits-description "A descent to the west leads back to the Serpent Dunes, while to the east, the landscape starts to slope into a wide valley. A narrow path winds its way to the south, towards a mysterious ruin.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The sun bleaches the plateau to a bone-white expanse.", :night "The plateau under the moonlight is an endless silver sheet, the lone tree casting a long shadow.", :dawn "The light of dawn sets the plateau aglow with a warm ochre hue.", :dusk "As the day fades, the plateau is draped in the purples and reds of sunset."}, :season {:summer "The heat of summer turns the plateau into a natural oven.", :winter "The winter cold makes the sandstone plateau feel almost like a frozen lake.", :fall "Sparse, brittle leaves fall from the acacia tree, disappearing into the winds.", :spring "Tiny blossoms appear on the acacia, dots of color on the monotonous plateau."}, :weather {:rain "The rain darkens the plateau, each drop echoing in the vast silence.", :snow "A layer of snow turns the plateau into a blank canvas, broken only by the lone tree.", :fog "The plateau shrouded in fog seems even more otherworldly.", :sunny "The glare off the plateau is blinding under the fierce sun.", :cloudy "Clouds cast moving shadows across the plateau, an ever-changing landscape.", :partly-cloudy "The patchy sunlight on the plateau creates a mosaic of light and shadow."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 2}, :flags #{}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 4}, :flags #{}}, :south {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 21}, :flags #{:door}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 4}, :title "Valley of the Whispering Winds", :description "A wide valley stretches out here, the sand dunes giving way to scattered rocks and sparse vegetation. The winds seem to gather here, rustling through the brittle shrubs and creating haunting, whispering sounds. Despite the arid conditions, the valley has a desolate beauty of its own.", :exits-description "A slow ascent to the west leads back to the Silent Plateau, while to the east, the valley narrows into a tight gorge. A rocky path winds northwards to a secluded oasis.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The valley seems to shimmer under the harsh sunlight.", :night "The valley under the moon is filled with long shadows and whispering winds.", :dawn "The first rays of sunlight touch the valley, casting it in a soft glow.", :dusk "The setting sun casts a dramatic play of light and shadow in the valley."}, :season {:summer "The dry heat seems to suck all moisture from the valley air.", :winter "The rocks in the valley are touched with frost in the cold winter mornings.", :fall "The wind seems to pick up in the valley, carrying with it the whisper of autumn.", :spring "Small flowers poke out from the hardy shrubs, a sign of spring's arrival."}, :weather {:rain "The rare rain brings a temporary vibrancy to the valley.", :snow "Snow dusts the valley, settling on rocks and shrubs.", :fog "The valley is quiet, the fog muffling the usual whispering winds.", :sunny "The sun highlights the subtle colors in the rock formations of the valley.", :cloudy "The valley seems more somber under the overcast sky.", :partly-cloudy "The partly cloudy sky creates a patchwork of shadows in the valley."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 3}, :flags #{}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 5}, :flags #{}}, :north {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 22}, :flags #{:door}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 5}, :title "Echoing Gorge", :description "The valley narrows into a deep, winding gorge, its steep walls echoing the faintest sounds. Striated layers of rock tell the story of ages past. A sense of quiet solitude pervades this secluded corner of the desert.", :exits-description "The mouth of the gorge lies to the west, leading back to the Valley of the Whispering Winds. The gorge deepens as it winds to the east, seemingly leading to a hidden cavern.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The walls of the gorge reflect the harsh sunlight, painting the rocks in hues of orange and red.", :night "The gorge is filled with shadows under the moonlight, creating an aura of mystery.", :dawn "The first rays of light play across the gorge, creating a symphony of colors.", :dusk "As the sun sets, the gorge is bathed in a wash of warm hues, casting long shadows."}, :season {:summer "The heat is more pronounced within the confines of the gorge, the rocks radiating the day's warmth.", :winter "The gorge offers some protection from the winter chill, its walls blocking the wind.", :fall "The echo of wind howling through the gorge is the desert's lonesomeness amplified.", :spring "Scant spring flowers bloom in the crevices of the gorge, adding splashes of color to the rocks."}, :weather {:rain "The echo of raindrops pattering on the rocks fills the gorge with a rhythmic melody.", :snow "The snowfall quiets the echoes in the gorge, its walls blanketed in white.", :fog "Fog in the gorge muffles the echoes, making the solitude even more profound.", :sunny "The bright sun casts stark shadows in the gorge, emphasizing its depth.", :cloudy "Cloudy skies deepen the shadows in the gorge, giving it a subdued ambience.", :partly-cloudy "The spotty sunlight plays across the gorge's walls, creating a shifting pattern of light and shadow."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 4}, :flags #{}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 6}, :flags #{}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 6}, :title "The Hidden Cavern", :description "Hidden deep within the Echoing Gorge, the cavern is a secret sanctuary of the desert. Stalactites and stalagmites create an otherworldly landscape in the semi-darkness. A faint trickle of water can be heard somewhere in the depths, the promise of life beneath the arid desert.", :exits-description "The only way out of the cavern leads west, back through the Echoing Gorge.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "Rays of sunlight reach into the cavern, bouncing off the damp walls.", :night "The cavern takes on a gloomy atmosphere under the moonlight.", :dawn "The muted morning light barely reaches the interior of the cavern.", :dusk "The setting sun paints the cavern's entrance in a warm palette of reds and oranges."}, :season {:summer "The cavern is surprisingly cool compared to the heat outside.", :winter "The cavern offers a respite from the winter's chill.", :fall "The cavern remains unchanged despite the turning of the seasons.", :spring "Drips of water become more frequent, hinting at an underground spring."}, :weather {:rain "The sound of rain resonates within the cavern, a soothing lullaby.", :snow "The cavern entrance is half-obscured by the falling snow.", :fog "Fog rolls into the cavern, creating a surreal, dreamlike atmosphere.", :sunny "Bright sunlight at the cavern's entrance casts long shadows within.", :cloudy "The lack of sunlight makes the cavern seem more quiet and introspective.", :partly-cloudy "Flashes of sunlight appear and disappear at the cavern's entrance."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 5}, :flags #{:hidden}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 7}, :title "The Dusty Mirage", :description "This stretch of desert is known for creating deceiving mirages, teasing travellers with visions of water. Shifting sand dunes spread out in all directions, their forms constantly changing with the winds. An eerie silence engulfs the landscape, broken only by the faint whispering of the wind.", :exits-description "Trails of sand lead back west to the Serpent Dunes. To the east, the desert seems to merge with the horizon, endless and daunting. To the north, the silhouette of an ancient obelisk breaks the monotony of the landscape.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The midday sun creates an illusion of shimmering water on the horizon.", :night "The moon casts an ethereal light over the dunes, deepening the mirage effect.", :dawn "At dawn, the sand dunes look like waves on a golden sea, adding to the deception.", :dusk "The setting sun tinges the mirage with hues of red and purple."}, :season {:summer "The heat intensifies the mirage, the illusion of water becoming almost palpable.", :winter "The winter chill does little to dispel the illusion created by the mirage.", :fall "In fall, the mirage sometimes takes on the color of the autumn leaves.", :spring "In spring, the mirage appears more vivid, a cruel tease in the arid desert."}, :weather {:rain "Raindrops seem to vanish as they hit the mirage, adding to its mystery.", :snow "Snowflakes swirl around the mirage, a surreal sight in the desert.", :fog "Fog creates a mystical aura around the mirage, blurring its boundaries.", :sunny "Bright sunlight heightens the mirage, making it look more tantalizing.", :cloudy "Under a cloudy sky, the mirage seems less vivid, yet retains its deceptive allure.", :partly-cloudy "The mirage flickers under the shifting sunlight, appearing and disappearing with the clouds."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 1}, :flags #{}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 8}, :flags #{}}, :north {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 23}, :flags #{:door :hidden}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 8}, :title "The Endless Horizon", :description "Here, the desert seems to extend indefinitely, merging with the horizon. It's a daunting vista of shifting sands and relentless heat. In this vast emptiness, time seems to stand still, creating a feeling of timeless desolation.", :exits-description "Looking back west, the Dusty Mirage shimmers tantalizingly. To the east, a cluster of stone formations breaks the flat monotony.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The vast expanse of desert is overwhelming under the midday sun.", :night "Under the starry sky, the desert takes on an ethereal beauty.", :dawn "The dawn paints the endless desert in a soft, warm glow.", :dusk "As the sun sets, the desert becomes a sea of shadows, the horizon barely distinguishable."}, :season {:summer "The summer heat is relentless, making the desert even more inhospitable.", :winter "Even the winter's chill seems to be swallowed by the vastness of the desert.", :fall "The fall winds whip up sandstorms, blurring the horizon even further.", :spring "Spring brings a subtle change, the sand taking on a slightly softer hue."}, :weather {:rain "Rain is a rare event here, but when it happens, it creates an astonishing spectacle against the horizon.", :snow "Snow on the endless desert is a surreal sight, the white blanketing the endless sands.", :fog "Fog makes the desert seem even more endless, the horizon lost in the mist.", :sunny "Under the bright sun, the horizon appears to shimmer, a deceiving mirage of its own.", :cloudy "Cloudy skies cast the desert in a more somber light, yet its vastness remains unchanged.", :partly-cloudy "The desert under a partly cloudy sky is a dance of shadow and light."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 7}, :flags #{}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 9}, :flags #{}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 9}, :title "Stone Sentinel Formations", :description "Towering stone formations rise from the desert, standing like silent sentinels against the sands. Their rugged, weather-beaten faces are etched with the testament of time. Shadows cast by the formations provide rare respite from the unrelenting desert sun.", :exits-description "The endless expanse of the desert lies to the west. To the east, a narrow canyon winds its way through the rocks.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The sunlight creates stark shadows, casting the formations in dramatic relief.", :night "Moonlight softens the harsh lines of the formations, imbuing them with an ethereal beauty.", :dawn "As the sun rises, the formations are bathed in a warm, golden light.", :dusk "The setting sun turns the stones a deep, fiery red."}, :season {:summer "The heat makes the stones hot to touch, almost as if they're alive.", :winter "In winter, the stones retain a residual chill, providing a cool touch in the arid desert.", :fall "The stones appear even more stark against the backdrop of fall's muted palette.", :spring "The sparse spring flora adds touches of green to the otherwise barren formations."}, :weather {:rain "Rain brings out the rich colors of the stones, their surfaces gleaming wetly.", :snow "Snowfall adds an unexpected softness to the formations, turning them into monolithic snow sculptures.", :fog "In fog, the formations loom like mysterious giants, their outlines blurred.", :sunny "The sun casts the formations in a harsh light, emphasizing their grandeur.", :cloudy "The overcast sky adds a somber note to the formations, enhancing their silent vigil.", :partly-cloudy "Shadows shift constantly on the stones under a partly cloudy sky, creating an ever-changing tableau."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 8}, :flags #{}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 10}, :flags #{}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 10}, :title "The Narrow Canyon", :description "A narrow canyon cuts through the stone formations, its walls reaching up towards the sky. A rare trickle of water can be found here, carving its way through the rocks over countless years. The canyon's twists and turns create an intricate labyrinth within the desert.", :exits-description "The canyon opens to the west onto the Stone Sentinel Formations. The passage narrows further to the east, leading into a hidden grotto.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The sunlight filters through the canyon, creating a play of light and shadow.", :night "The canyon is bathed in a soft moonlight, creating an atmosphere of quiet tranquility.", :dawn "The first light of day gradually illuminates the canyon, revealing its intricate beauty.", :dusk "As dusk falls, the canyon is cast in an array of soft, warm hues."}, :season {:summer "The canyon offers some respite from the summer heat, its walls providing much-needed shade.", :winter "The chill seems to cling to the canyon's walls, providing a refreshing contrast to the desert heat.", :fall "The whisper of the wind through the canyon is the desert's solitude made tangible.", :spring "Traces of spring life can be seen in the hardy plants that manage to thrive in the canyon's nooks."}, :weather {:rain "Rainwater collects in the canyon's crevices, creating small, transient pools.", :snow "Snow dusts the canyon's walls, softening their ruggedness.", :fog "Fog in the canyon creates a sense of mystery, its depths shrouded in a soft mist.", :sunny "The narrow sliver of sky visible from the canyon is a bright blue against the stone walls.", :cloudy "The canyon feels more enclosed under a cloudy sky, the walls seeming to close in.", :partly-cloudy "The shifting clouds create a dynamic interplay of light and shadow within the canyon."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 9}, :flags #{}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 11}, :flags #{:door :locked}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 11}, :title "Hidden Grotto", :description "Concealed within the canyon's labyrinth lies a hidden grotto. An underground stream surfaces here, filling the air with the sound of gently flowing water. The walls of the grotto are adorned with ancient pictographs, telling tales of a time long past.", :exits-description "The narrow canyon lies to the west, while a concealed passage to the north seems to lead to a concealed oasis.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "Sunlight streams through a crack in the grotto's ceiling, illuminating the ancient drawings.", :night "In the dim moonlight, the pictographs on the walls take on a mysterious aura.", :dawn "The first light of the day reveals the grotto in its tranquil beauty.", :dusk "The setting sun casts a reddish glow on the grotto's walls, bringing out the colors in the pictographs."}, :season {:summer "The grotto provides a cool retreat from the summer heat, the water refreshing to touch.", :winter "Despite the winter chill outside, the grotto maintains a surprisingly mild temperature.", :fall "The subtle changes in the desert light during fall create different hues in the grotto.", :spring "The sound of the stream is more lively in spring, as if echoing the season's renewal."}, :weather {:rain "The sound of rain on the grotto's entrance adds to the peaceful ambiance within.", :snow "When it snows, the grotto becomes a cozy refuge, a world away from the cold desert.", :fog "Fog seeping into the grotto creates an air of enchantment, as if the place exists out of time.", :sunny "The sunlight glinting off the water creates shimmering patterns on the grotto's walls.", :cloudy "Under a cloudy sky, the grotto feels more enclosed, yet there's a comforting sense of solitude.", :partly-cloudy "The intermittent sunlight streaming into the grotto brings the pictographs to life."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 10}, :flags #{:door :locked}}, :north {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 12}, :flags #{:hidden}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 12}, :title "Secret Oasis", :description "This secret oasis is a vibrant pocket of life within the arid desert. Tall palm trees ring a clear pond fed by an underground stream. Verdant grasses and vibrant flowers add a splash of color to the sandy landscape.", :exits-description "A hidden passage to the south leads back to the Hidden Grotto. To the east, the oasis is bounded by a towering dune.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The sunlight creates sparkling reflections in the pond, bringing a touch of magic to the oasis.", :night "The night descends on the oasis with a peaceful hush, broken only by the soft rustle of palm fronds.", :dawn "The morning light imbues the oasis with a serene beauty, every detail vivid and fresh.", :dusk "As the day fades, the oasis takes on a quiet charm, the setting sun painting the scene in soft hues."}, :season {:summer "The summer heat makes the oasis even more inviting, the cool water a balm for weary travelers.", :winter "Despite the winter's chill, the oasis retains its vitality, a testament to the resilience of nature.", :fall "As fall descends, the oasis seems to stand against the season, its vibrant colors undiminished.", :spring "Spring brings a burst of new growth to the oasis, enhancing its lush beauty."}, :weather {:rain "Rain showers turn the oasis into a symphony of sounds, from the patter of drops on leaves to the ripples in the pond.", :snow "Snowflakes add a surprising touch to the oasis, creating a scene of stark contrast.", :fog "The oasis shrouded in fog becomes a mystical haven, its details softly obscured.", :sunny "Under the bright sun, the oasis is a vibrant tableau of life amid the desert.", :cloudy "Cloudy skies cast a soft light over the oasis, bringing out the subtleties in its colors.", :partly-cloudy "Partly cloudy skies create a dynamic interplay of light and shadow, lending the oasis an ever-changing charm."}}, :exits {:south {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 11}, :flags #{:hidden}}, :east {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 13}, :flags #{}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 13}, :title "Towering Dune", :description "A colossal sand dune rises next to the oasis, its sandy slopes shifting and glittering under the sky. The view from atop is breathtaking, offering a panoramic sight of the endless desert expanse. The wind constantly alters the dune's shape, creating intricate patterns on its surface.", :exits-description "To the west is the vibrant Secret Oasis. To the north, the dune descends back to the desert floor.", :special-descriptions {:time {:day "The bright sunlight causes the dune to gleam, a golden monolith amidst the sandy expanse.", :night "Bathed in moonlight, the dune appears to be a silver mountain, its outlines soft under the starry sky.", :dawn "The first rays of the rising sun set the dune ablaze, an ethereal glow gradually taking over.", :dusk "As the sun sets, the dune takes on hues of red and orange, a fiery landmark against the deepening sky."}, :season {:summer "The summer sun intensifies the heat radiating off the dune, making it a formidable presence.", :winter "The winter cold tempers the dune, its normally hot surface comfortably warm to the touch.", :fall "The winds of fall create intricate patterns on the dune, the sand shifting and resettling.", :spring "With spring, the occasional sprouting of hardy desert flowers creates surprising pops of color on the dune."}, :weather {:rain "Rainfall on the dune creates a rare spectacle, the droplets momentarily transforming sand into reflective pearls.", :snow "A dusting of snow on the dune creates a striking contrast, the white layer a stark anomaly.", :fog "Fog around the dune gives it an aura of mystery, the monumental mass looming through the mist.", :sunny "The bright sun brings out the dune's golden hues, the grains of sand sparkling under the radiant light.", :cloudy "The cloudy skies over the dune cast a moody light, the sandy giant standing somber and grand.", :partly-cloudy "Under a partly cloudy sky, the dune appears as an ever-changing painting, shadows moving across its surface."}}, :exits {:west {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 12}, :flags #{}}, :north {:to-room-id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 14}, :flags #{}}}} {:id {:zone-id "arid-desert02", :room-num 14}, :title "Desert Floor", :description "From the base of the towering dune, the flat desert floor stretche